text: yeung ban nhek tukasamoutr daembi aoy ambaur aisreael ban daer chhlangphot haey hvie r aon ning teahean robsa ke ban tam pikraoy puokke daoy kar karbampean ning pheap chea sa trauv . louh nowpel del tuk ban lich krobadandab ke( hvie r aon) teub ke niyeay tha khnhom ban chue haey tha pitabrakd nasa kmean mcheasa na del trauv ke korp da pitabrakd krawpi mcheasa del ambaur aisreael ban chue leu trong noh laey . haey khnhom ka sthet knongchamnaom anak mou slei m der
